  <title><literal>DBget()</literal></title>

  <indexterm significance="preferred">
    <primary>Dialplan-Applikationen</primary>

    <secondary><code>DBget()</code></secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <simpara>Reads a value from the Asterisk database (AstDB).</simpara>

  <synopsis>DBget(<replaceable>variable</replaceable>=<replaceable>family</replaceable>/<replaceable>key</replaceable>|<replaceable>options</replaceable>)</synopsis>

  <important>
    <para><literal>DBget()</literal> is removed as of Asterisk 1.4 and has
    been replaced by the <literal>DB()</literal> (<xref
    linkend="functions-db" />) function.</para>
  </important>

